There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter—(1) $500,000 for fiscal year 2010; and

(2) such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 2011 through 2014.

(Pub. L. 111–19, § 5, May 12, 2009, 123 Stat. 1615.)</akn:p></akn:content><akn:subsection eId="subsec_80s_3_1"><akn:num>(1)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(1) $500,000 for fiscal year 2010; and</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_80s_3_2"><akn:num>(2)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(2) such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 2011 through 2014.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection></akn:section></akn:body></akn:act></akn:akomaNtoso>